    <item>
      <title>司法部限制其对州选举的权力</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/06/11/us/politics/trump-california-vote-elections-investigations.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[该部门曾试图避免参与州选举，并敦促谨慎行事。随着特朗普总统重申其毫无根据的选举不可信的断言，该机构现在正在推进欺诈指控。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/06/11/us/politics/trump-california-vote-elections-investigations.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 11 Jun 2026 19:44:49 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
